{"tid":1985606,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"晤傳媒時嚴重手震　並非首次　聶德權健康受關注","createTime":"2020-04-23T09:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T09:08:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a745a4ce3ba59ab39c39f2d75b23777710e011fc","tid":1985606,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"剛被任命公務員事務局局長聶德權今天在立法會見記者期間，右手有嚴重手震情況。據香港電台報道，當時聶德權他正以英文回應有關《基本法》第22條的問題，雙手於身後交疊，其後他以中文回應另一提問時，亦有手震。今天是聶德權首次以公務員事務局局長身分在立法會回應傳媒提問。<br />\n<br />\n今次並非聶德權有手震情況，上月 4 日他代表特區政府前往武漢，以包機接當地港人回港，在機場禮賓通道見傳媒時，放在身後的手同樣有嚴重手震。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向公務員事務局查詢聶德權的手震現象及健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=229372691836026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D229372691836026&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6pj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=2dfc546c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/watch/?v=229372691836026</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%99%A4%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E6%99%82%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%89%8B%E9%9C%87-%E4%B8%A6%E9%9D%9E%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1-%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%8F%97%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259C%2587-%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%2F&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6pj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=33690f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259C%2587-%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2581%25A5%25E